
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .header { padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; background-color: #f8f8f8; }
        .content { padding: 30px 20px; line-height: 1.6; text-align: left; }
        .summary { background-color: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #eee; padding: 15px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .footer { padding: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #777; background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="DevGo Logo" style="width: 150px; height: auto;" />
            <h2 style="margin-top: 10px;">Your Parcel is Booked!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{customerName}},</p>

            <p>Thank you for booking with DevGo! Your parcel is confirmed and will be picked up soon.</p>

            <div class="summary">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Booking Summary</h3>
                <p><strong>Tracking Number:</strong> {{trackingNumber}}</p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{status}}</p>
                <p><strong>Pickup From:</strong> {{pickupAddress}}</p>
                <p><strong>Deliver To:</strong> {{deliveryAddress}}</p>
                <p><strong>Total Charges:</strong> Rs. {{deliveryCharge}}</p>
                <p><strong>Payment Method:</strong> {{paymentMethod}}</p>
            </div>
            

            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">You can track your parcel's live status on our website using the tracking number.</p>

            <p>Thanks for choosing DevGo!<br>
            <strong>The DevGo Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 DevGo. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>